                    be applied to DITA or non-DITA resources: <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/dita-main-files.html#dita-main-files__moving_or_renaming_nondita_resources" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="xref:2;24:57"/></li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="li:2;25:21">
                    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="p:3;26:24">In the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:4;26:42">DITA Maps Manager</uicontrol> view you can arrange the
