                </li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="li:3;31:21">There are refactoring actions for converting between DITA topic types. So, if
                    the resulting topics look more like <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="b:4;32:60">DITA Tasks</b> or <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="b:5;32:81">DITA Concepts</b>,
                    you can simply convert them using refactoring actions like <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:5;33:91">Convert to
                        Task</uicontrol>, <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:6;34:54">Convert to Concept</uicontrol> and others.</li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="li:4;35:21">There are actions for generating unique IDs for elements (<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:7;35:90">Generate
