                        (<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:8;37:37">Change topic ID to file name</uicontrol>).</li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="li:5;38:21">When resulting documents contain <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="i:1;38:57">nested topics</i> or <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="i:2;38:81">sections</i>, you
