                        <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:10;40:36">Convert Sections to New Topics</uicontrol> to extract new
                    files.</li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="li:6;42:21">Topics can be extracted from the map hierarchy into a new DITA map, using the
