                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="li:7;44:21">
                    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="p:4;45:24">The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="b:6;45:31">Convert DITA Map to Bookmap</b> and <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:12;45:78">Convert Bookmap to DITA
                            Map</uicontrol> actions allow converting between map and bookmap
                        types.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="li:8;49:21">
                    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="p:5;50:24">For converting links inside your documents from <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="i:3;50:75">direct addressing</i> to
                            <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="i:4;51:32">indirect key-based addressing</i>, you can use the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="b:7;51:86">Define keys for
                            all topic references</b> action.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="li:9;54:21">There are also operations for modifying elements inside documents: <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/predefined-refactoring-operations-x-tools.html#predefined-refactoring-operations__refactoring_operations_for_elements" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="xref:4;56:57"/></li>
            </ul>In the main menu <menucascade class="+ topic/ph ui-d/menucascade " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/migrating_word_to_dita_bdc/customizing_the_resulting_dita_content.dita" xtrc="menucascade:1;57:48">
